<paragraph id="IFRS09_6.3.1" base="SL32570229" principles="yes"><paranum>6.3.1</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 9"/><data name="paranum" value="6.3.1"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS09_P0436">A hedged item can be a recognised asset or liability, an unrecognised <xref base="F32570687" href="IFRS09_APPA.dita#IFRS09_APPA/IFRS09_P0709"><i>firm commitment</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0131"/></ph></xref>, a <xref base="F32570691" href="IFRS09_APPA.dita#IFRS09_APPA/IFRS09_P0711"><i>forecast transaction</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0138"/></ph></xref> or a net investment in a foreign operation. The hedged item can be:</p><ol id="IFRS09_L0048" base="SL32570233" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS09_P0437" base="SL32570235">a single item; or</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS09_P0438" base="SL32570237">a group of items (subject to <xref id="IFRS09_X0683" base="F68315518" href="IFRS09_g6.6.1-6.6.6.dita#IFRS09_g6.6.1-6.6.6/IFRS09_g6.6.1-6.6.6_TI">paragraphs 6.6.1&#x2013;6.6.6</xref> and <xref id="IFRS09_X0684" base="F68315519" href="IFRS09_g6.6.1-6.6.6.dita#IFRS09_g6.6.1-6.6.6/IFRS09_g6.6.1-6.6.6_TI">B6.6.1&#x2013;B6.6.16</xref>).</p></li></ol><p id="IFRS09_P0439" base="SL32570238">A hedged item can also be a component of such an item or group of items (see <xref id="IFRS09_X0685" base="F68315520" href="IFRS09_g6.3.7-6.3.7.dita#IFRS09_g6.3.7-6.3.7/IFRS09_g6.3.7-6.3.7_TI">paragraphs 6.3.7</xref> and <xref id="IFRS09_X0686" base="F68315561" href="IFRS09_gB6.3.7-B6.3.25.dita#IFRS09_gB6.3.7-B6.3.25/IFRS09_gB6.3.7-B6.3.25_TI">B6.3.7&#x2013;B6.3.25</xref>).</p></body></paragraph>